data.description: This turnkey, 4-bedroom single-story residence is perfect for those seeking easy living without compromising on style! With its updated features and single-story layout, this home is a true standout in the market. The open-concept design makes this home feel spacious and inviting. The kitchen is a dream! Granite countertops, stainless steel appliances – it has everything you would want. The restrooms are both highly upgraded with new showers and granite countertops. The backyard is now a great space for all of your outdoor entertaining needs.
